sequenceDiagram
    participant DeploySH as deploy.sh<br/>(Init Container)
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Namespace as redhat-ods-applications<br/>Namespace
    participant KfDef as KfDef CRs<br/>(8-9 resources)
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>Kubernetes Watch
    participant Components as Component<br/>Deployments

    Note over DeploySH,Components: Flow 1: Deployer Bootstraps RHODS Platform

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: oc apply (namespaces, CRDs, configs)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Created
    DeploySH->>Namespace: oc apply (dashboard config, ISV tiles,<br/>network policies, RBAC bindings)
    DeploySH->>KfDef: oc apply KfDef CRs<br/>(dashboard, nbc, modelmesh, dspo,<br/>notebooks, monitoring, anaconda)
    Operator->>KfDef: Watch KfDef CRs<br/>Auth: Operator SA token
    Operator->>Components: Apply manifests from<br/>/opt/manifests/odh-manifests.tar.gz

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP
    participant ClusterProm as prometheus-k8s<br/>openshift-monitoring<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Metrics as Component Metrics<br/>Endpoints 8080/TCP
    participant BBE as Blackbox Exporter<br/>9115/TCP HTTP
    participant Dashboard as rhods-dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AM as Alertmanager<br/>9093/TCP
    participant PD as PagerDuty API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SMTP as SMTP Server<br/>TLS
    participant DMS as Dead Man's Snitch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Prom,DMS: Flow 2: Prometheus Monitoring Pipeline

    Prom->>ClusterProm: Federated scrape<br/>HTTPS/TLS (service CA)<br/>Auth: Bearer token (SA)
    ClusterProm-->>Prom: haproxy, controller_runtime,<br/>container, kubelet metrics

    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape component metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (no TLS, no auth)
    Metrics-->>Prom: notebook-controller, model-controller,<br/>modelmesh, DSPO metrics

    Prom->>BBE: Scrape blackbox metrics<br/>HTTP/9115 (no TLS)
    BBE->>Dashboard: Probe dashboard availability<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer token (SA)
    Dashboard-->>BBE: Probe result (SLO check)
    BBE-->>Prom: Probe success/failure metrics

    Note over AM,DMS: Alert Routing (Managed Service Only)

    AM->>PD: Critical alerts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service key
    AM->>SMTP: User notification emails<br/>(PVC usage warnings)<br/>SMTP/TLS, SMTP credentials
    AM->>DMS: Continuous heartbeat<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: None
